bin		    link to /usr/bin
sbin		link to /usr/sbin
home		where all user directories are located
dev		    files of all devices
usr/bin		contains binary files 
usr/sbin 	contains binary files of super user
boot 		contains boot files
tmp		    contains temporary files(log files, cache files)
root 		administrator
etc		    contain settings files
media		mount drives
mnt		    explicitly mount drives

